{"tid":1502500,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩手足之間，以禮待人","createTime":"2019-08-24T16:34:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T17:06:46.000Z","uid":217593,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5607d14c8333bf7e3027a20de690b3c05e1e32ab","tid":1502500,"uid":217593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:34:17.000Z","msg":"知道大家經過哩兩個幾月，<br />\n大家都好攰，好嬲。<br />\n但麻煩大家唔好將個人嘅情緒，<br />\n釋放喺其他手足，甚至係路人到，<br />\n大家係手足，而唔係出氣袋。<br />\n手足之間有商有量，<br />\n對住手足就nice啲！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不篤灰、不割席、不指責</span></span>"},{"pid":"ea7856c599dc4b181fae31d8d75cf8e0693f3c8b","tid":1502500,"uid":217593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:46:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6f61d6bd3250094358665a6bf41501692760125","tid":1502500,"uid":217593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:46:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52db70e4bcfd419a7a66d90f2faa76ff17b1babb","tid":1502500,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:47:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9c14a72344de2f6dc3d12561b3f504fa86b4b46","tid":1502500,"uid":217593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:47:49.000Z","msg":"以禮相待<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a515aa13b7e2d7d0e135485741fd6e1686cd36d5","tid":1502500,"uid":217593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:52:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9a28c82a8bb4dc15129aa757dc31db13b2ebdb5","tid":1502500,"uid":217593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:59:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc54d5a98ad7f4aed5a00ab7e7ffaa76b1f8edcc","tid":1502500,"uid":217593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:59:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b0f15626